{{Quote|Can you dig out some of the bore-bangs from that pack, please? Four should do it.''"<br />"''What are they?''"<br />"''The long red sticks. Custom ordnance.|RC-1136 and Etain Tur-Mukan|<ref name="Republic Commando: Hard Contact">''[[Republic Commando: Hard Contact]]''</ref>}}
'''Bore bangs''' were long red sticks of explosive that could bury themselves several meters underground. They were used by [[Clone commando/Legends|clone commando]] [[Darman Skirata|Darman]] to great effect during [[Omega Squad]]'s [[Mission to Qiilura|mission]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Qiilura/Legends|Qiilura]]. When he and [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]] [[Etain Tur-Mukan]] were being chased by [[Battle droid/Legends|battle droids]], he used bore bangs to blow away a hillside to eliminate his pursuers.

